ActDepartment of Industry Act
SubjectNational Aboriginal Economic Development Appointment Process and Name Change
PrecisOrder approving the amendments, by the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development, to the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board Order in order to (1) remove the reference to appointment of members by the Governor in Council and to add a reference indicating that the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development is to make appointments; and (2) change the legal name of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board to the National Indigenous Economic Development Board.
